<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5"> منكر بزيادة:</span> <span class="c2">((ولجيرانهم)</span>) ـ <span class="c2">((الضعيفة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٦٣٩٩)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
